flowchart LR
    Dev[Desenvolvedor do jogo] --> Editor[MomoRogue.Editor]
    Editor --> Project[Projeto .mrgproj]
    Editor --> Runtime[MomoRogue.Runtime]
    Editor --> BuildTool[MomoRogue.BuildTool]
    BuildTool --> Dotnet[dotnet publish]
    BuildTool --> Installer[WiX / Instalador]
    Runtime --> Engine[MomoRogue.Engine]
    Runtime --> Adapter[MomoRogue.SadConsole]
